# Project Structure

This is a Next.js web application for a crypto casino gaming platform called "Somnia Pumpaz" that operates on the Somnia Network.

## Main Directories

- `/src/app`: Next.js app router pages and layouts
  - Main entry point is [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx)
  - Root layout is [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
  - Dashboard features are in [src/app/dashboard](mdc:src/app/dashboard)
  - Smart contract ABIs are in [src/app/contracts/contract.ts](mdc:src/app/contracts/contract.ts)

- `/src/components`: Reusable UI components
  - Common components like header and menu are in [src/components/common](mdc:src/components/common)
  - Game-specific components like [src/components/coin.tsx](mdc:src/components/coin.tsx) and [src/components/die.tsx](mdc:src/components/die.tsx)
  - Web3 provider is [src/components/web3Provider.tsx](mdc:src/components/web3Provider.tsx)

- `/src/redux`: Redux store for state management
  - Main store configuration is [src/redux/store.ts](mdc:src/redux/store.ts)
  - Feature-specific slices like coinFlip, diceGame, etc.

- `/public`: Static assets like images and icons
  - Images in [public/images](mdc:public/images)
  - Icons in [public/icons](mdc:public/icons)

## Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts): Next.js configuration
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts): Tailwind CSS configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript configuration
